	<chapter id="ch1">
		<page id="pageIntro">
			<p underline="true" bold="true" align="center" space="20">Introduction</p>
			<p space="10">The ancient D'ni people have known the Art of Writing for countless millenia, and now this knowledge will be passed on to you! "Linking Through the Ages" was written by TheFloydman and is divided into two parts:</p>
			<p space="10">The first half covers the basics of how to craft Linking Books and Descriptive Books, the means by which you will Link (or warp) to countless Ages--worlds with varying seas, terrains, heavens, and treasures.</p>
			<p space="10">More details about how to write better Links can be found in the second half.</p>
			<p space="10">If you lose this book, you can craft a new one at any time:</p>
			<small_recipe_centered>
                <stack ore="dyeBlack" />
                <space />
                <stack item="minecraft:paper" />
                <space />
                <stack item="gbook:guidebook" />
            </small_recipe_centered>
		</page>
